import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; import jwt_decode from "jwt-decode"; const Navbar = () => { const [ name, setName] = useState(''); const [ expire, setExpire] = useState([]); const [ token, setToken] = useState([]); const navigate = useNavigate(); useEffect(() => { refreshToken() }, []) const refreshToken = async () => { try { const response = await axios.get('http://localhost:5000/token'); setToken(response.data.accessToken) const decoded = jwt_decode(response.data.accessToken); setName(decoded.name); setExpire(decoded.exp); } catch (error) { if(error.response){ navigate('/'); } } } return (
{/*
Sample Menu
My Profile Settings Messages
Log Out
*/}
{name}
My Profile Settings Messages
Log Out
About Log out
) } export default Navbar
